Summary:	High-level API for X Keyboard Extension
Name:		libxklavier
Version:	5.4
Release: 	16%{?dist}
License:	LGPLv2+
URL: http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/LibXklavier
BuildRequires: libxml2-devel
BuildRequires: libxkbfile-devel
